## How It Works

```
Intune triggers script as SYSTEM
        │
        ▼
Is SAS already installed?
   Yes → Exit 0 (Intune detects as compliant)
   No  ↓
        │
        ▼
Is an active user session present?
   No  → Exit, Intune retries later
   Yes ↓
        │
        ▼
Prompt user: Install now or postpone?
   Postpone → Write postpone marker, exit (Intune retries)
   Install  ↓
        │
        ▼
robocopy installer files from network share → C:\Temp\SAS_Install_2026\
        │
        ▼
Run setup.exe silently with response file
        │
        ▼
Write registry detection key
        │
        ▼
Log result, clean up temp files, exit
```

