## User Experience

When the script runs, the active user sees a dialog (delivered via `msg.exe` through `sysnative` to handle Intune's 32-bit execution context):

> **SAS 9.4 Installation**
> SAS 9.4 needs to be installed on your computer. Installation takes approximately 60 minutes. Please save your work.
> Click **Install Now** to begin, or **Postpone** to be reminded later.

- If the user postpones, Intune will retry on its next check-in cycle
- If no user is present, the script exits and Intune retries automatically
- If the prompt times out (1 hour), the script re-prompts rather than proceeding without consent

