## Logging

The script writes timestamped logs to two locations:

- **Local:** `C:\Intune_Logs\SAS_Install_2026_Logs\`
- **Network:** `\\your-fileserver\share\Logs\SAS_Install_2026_Logs\` *(falls back gracefully if unavailable)*

Log entries are structured for easy filtering:

```
2026-02-27 10:45:12 [INFO]    SAS not detected - installation needed
